{"id": "art-380", "label": "Art. 380", "title": "Art. 380: Statutele speciale", "slug": "art-380", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 380: Statutele speciale </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Pot beneficia de statute speciale func&#355;ionarii publici care\nîndeplinesc activit&#259;&#355;ile prev&#259;zute la art. 370 alin. (3) în\ncadrul:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)structurilor\nde specialitate ale Parlamentului României;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)structurilor\nde specialitate ale Administra&#355;iei Preziden&#355;iale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>c)structurilor\nde specialitate ale Consiliului Legislativ;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>d)serviciilor\ndiplomatice &#351;i consulare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>e)institu&#355;iilor\ndin sistemul de ordine public&#259; &#351;i securitate na&#355;ional&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>f)structurilor\nvamale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>g)altor\nservicii publice stabilite prin lege, care îndeplinesc activit&#259;&#355;ile\nprev&#259;zute la art. 370 alin. (3) lit. h).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_206525000\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1354\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_206525000\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Prin excep&#355;ie de la prevederile alin. (1), în\ncadrul structurilor prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) lit. e) &#351;i f) pot\nbeneficia de statute speciale &#351;i func&#355;ionarii publici care\nîndeplinesc activit&#259;&#355;ile prev&#259;zute la art. 370 alin. (2).</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Prin excep&#355;ie de la\nprevederile art. 382 lit. d) &#351;i f), precum &#351;i prin excep&#355;ie de\nla alin. (1), în cadrul structurilor prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) lit. e) pot fi\nfunc&#355;ionari publici &#351;i pot beneficia de statute speciale persoanele\ncare î&#351;i desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; activitatea în unit&#259;&#355;ile de\nînv&#259;&#355;&#259;mânt &#351;i cele sanitare care &#355;in de acestea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Prin statutele speciale prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) se pot reglementa:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)drepturi,\nîndatoriri &#351;i incompatibilit&#259;&#355;i specifice, altele decât cele\nprev&#259;zute de prezenta parte;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)func&#355;ii\npublice specifice.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_60315954\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1353\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_60315954\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În cazul\nstatutelor speciale aplicabile serviciilor diplomatice &#351;i consulare,\ninstitu&#355;iilor din sistemul de ordine public&#259; &#351;i securitate\nna&#355;ional&#259; &#351;i structurilor vamale, dispozi&#355;iile speciale pot\nreglementa, pe lâng&#259; aspectele prev&#259;zute la alin. (4), &#351;i:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_456390875\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1352\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_456390875\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)cadrul legal special al raporturilor de serviciu;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1187282981\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1351\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1187282981\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)managementul carierei;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1007462608\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1350\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1007462608\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)regimul r&#259;spunderii administrative &#351;i\nmecanismele institu&#355;ionale specifice de aplicare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_429870979\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1349\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_429870979\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)gestiunea func&#355;iilor publice;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_50487844\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1348\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_50487844\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)mecanismele specifice care s&#259; asigure participarea\nfunc&#355;ionarilor publici la procesul decizional, prin aplicarea\ndispozi&#355;iilor privind constituirea comisiilor paritare &#351;i încheierea\nacordurilor colective.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}